<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="求多边形重心" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#求多边形重心" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 求多边形重心</h2>
<p>给定一个简单多边形，求其重心<br>
输入：多边形的顶点坐标（按逆时针顺序排列）<br>
输出：重心点C的坐标<br>
三角形的重心公式是：<br>
x=(x1+x2+x3)/3<br>
